\c 18
\s UMikhaya ukhuluma ngokunqotshwa kukaAhabi loJehoshafathi
\p
\v 1 Njalo uJehoshafathi wayelenotho lodumo ngobunengi\x + 17.5.\x*; wahlangana ngobuhlobo loAhabi\x + 21.6. 22.2. 2 Kho. 8.18.\x*.
\v 2 Ekupheleni kweminyaka wasesehlela kuAhabi\x + 1 Kho. 22.2-35.\x* eSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 16.24.\x*. UAhabi wamhlabela izimvu lenkabi ngobunengi, labantu ababelaye, wamncenga ukuthi enyukele\x + 18.31. 1 Kho. 21.25.\x* eRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 1 Kho. 22.3.\x*.
\v 3 UAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli wasesithi kuJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda: Uzahamba lami eRamothi-Gileyadi yini? Wasesithi kuye: Njengami unjalo wena, labantu bami banjengabantu bakho. Sizakuba lawe empini.
\v 4 UJehoshafathi wasesithi enkosini yakoIsrayeli: Akubuze lamuhla ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 5 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasibuthanisa abaprofethi, amadoda angamakhulu amane, yathi kubo: Sihambe yini eRamothi-Gileyadi empini kumbe ngiyekele? Basebesithi: Yenyuka, ngoba uNkulunkulu uza\add yi\add*nikela esandleni senkosi.
\v 6 Kodwa uJehoshafathi wathi: Kasekho yini lapha umprofethi weN\nd kosi\nd* ukuthi sibuze kuye?
\v 7 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: Kusekhona indoda eyodwa esingabuza ngayo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kodwa mina ngiyamzonda ngoba kaprofethi lutho oluhle ngami, kodwa okubi zonke izinsuku zakhe; lo nguMikhaya indodana kaImla. UJehoshafathi wasesithi: Inkosi ingatsho njalo.
\v 8 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasibiza umthenwa othile yathi: Landa masinyane uMikhaya indodana kaImla.
\p
\v 9 Njalo inkosi yakoIsrayeli loJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda babehlezi ngulowo lalowo esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi, begqoke izembatho, behlezi ebaleni engenelweni lesango leSamariya, bonke abaprofethi beprofetha-ke phambi kwabo.
\v 10 UZedekhiya indodana kaKhenahana wasezenzela impondo zensimbi, wathi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngalezi uzahlaba amaSiriya uze uwaqede.
\v 11 Labo bonke abaprofethi baprofetha njalo, besithi: Yenyukela eRamothi-Gileyadi uphumelele, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iza\add yi\add*nikela esandleni senkosi.
\p
\v 12 Isithunywa esasiyebiza uMikhaya sakhuluma kuye sisithi: Khangela, amazwi abaprofethi ngamlomo munye mahle enkosini; ngakho ilizwi lakho ake lifanane lelomunye wabo, ukhulume okuhle.
\v 13 Kodwa uMikhaya wathi: Kuphila kukaJehova, ngeqiniso lokho uNkulunkulu wami akutshoyo, lokho ngizakukhuluma.
\v 14 Esefikile enkosini, inkosi yathi kuye: Mikhaya, siye eRamothi-Gileyadi empini kumbe ngiyekele yini? Wasesithi: Yenyukani, liphumelele, ngoba bazanikelwa esandleni senu.
\v 15 Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Ngizakufungisa kuze kube yizikhathi ezingaki ukuze ungakhulumi kimi ngaphandle kweqiniso ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*?
\v 16 Wasesithi: Ngabona uIsrayeli wonke echithekile phezu kwezintaba njengezimvu ezingelamelusi; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Laba kabalamakhosi, kababuyele ngulowo endlini yakhe ngokuthula.
\v 17 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: Kangikutshelanga yini: Kayikuprofetha okuhle ngami kodwa okubi kuphela?
\v 18 Wasesithi: Ngakho zwanini ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*. Ngabona iN\nd kosi\nd* ihlezi esihlalweni sayo sobukhosi, lexuku lonke lamazulu limi ngakwesokunene sayo langakwesokhohlo sayo.
\v 19 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Ngubani ozahuga uAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli ukuze enyuke awe eRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 1 Kho. 22.20.\x*? Omunye wasekhuluma esitsho ngokunjalo, lomunye esitsho ngokunjalo.
\v 20 Kwasekuphuma umoya, wema phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: Mina ngizamhuga\x + 1 Kho. 22.20.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuwo: Ngani?
\v 21 Wasusithi: Ngizaphuma ngibe ngumoya wamanga emlonyeni wabo bonke abaprofethi bakhe. Yasisithi: Uza\add m\add*huga, njalo uzakuba lamandla; phuma wenze njalo\x + 1 Kho. 22.20.\x*.
\v 22 Ngakho-ke, khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* ifake umoya wamanga emlonyeni walababaprofethi bakho, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulume okubi ngawe.
\p
\v 23 UZedekhiya indodana kaKhenahana wasesondela, watshaya uMikhaya esihlathini, wathi: UMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wedlula ngandlela bani esuka kimi ukuthi akhulume lawe?
\v 24 UMikhaya wasesithi: Khangela, uzabona ngalolosuku mhla uzangena ekamelweni phakathi kwekamelo ukuthi ucatshe.
\v 25 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi: Thathani uMikhaya, limbuyisele kuAmoni umbusi womuzi lakuJowashi indodana yenkosi,
\v 26 lithi: Itsho njalo inkosi: Fakani lo entolongweni, limdlise isinkwa senhlupho lamanzi enhlupho ngize ngibuye ngokuthula.
\v 27 UMikhaya wasesithi: Uba ubuya lokubuya ngokuthula, iN\nd kosi\nd* izabe ingakhulumanga ngami. Wathi: Lalelani, bantu lonke.
\p
\v 28 Ngakho inkosi yakoIsrayeli loJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda benyukela eRamothi-Gileyadi.
\v 29 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasisithi kuJehoshafathi: Ngizazifihla isimo, ngingene empini, kodwa wena gqoka izembatho zakho. Inkosi yakoIsrayeli yasizifihla isimo, basebengena empini.
\v 30 Inkosi yeSiriya yayilayile-ke izinduna zenqola eyayilazo isithi: Lingalwi lomncane loba omkhulu, kodwa lenkosi yakoIsrayeli kuphela.
\v 31 Kwasekusithi induna zezinqola zibona uJehoshafathi zona zathi: Yena uyinkosi yakoIsrayeli. Ngakho zamhanqela ukulwa\x + 1 Kho. 22.32.\x*. Kodwa uJehoshafathi wahlaba umkhosi; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasimsiza\x + 1 Lan. 5.20.\x*\x + 1 Kho. 22.32.\x*. UNkulunkulu wazihuga zasuka kuye\x + 18.2.\x*.
\v 32 Ngoba kwathi lapho induna zezinqola zibona ukuthi kwakungayisiyo inkosi yakoIsrayeli, zaphenduka ekuyilandeleni.
\v 33 Umuntu \add othile\add* wasedonsa idandili engananzelele, wahlaba inkosi yakoIsrayeli phakathi kwenhlangano lebhatshi lensimbi; yasisithi kumtshayeli wenqola: Phendula isandla sakho, ungikhuphe ebuthweni, ngoba ngilimele.
\v 34 Impi yasikhula mhlalokho; inkosi yayisekelwe enqoleni iqondene lamaSiriya kwaze kwaba ntambama; yafa ngesikhathi sokutshona kwelanga.
